{"tid":1927206,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"豪氣！丹麥照顧受疫情衝擊行業 將負責七成五薪水","createTime":"2020-03-15T15:41:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-15T15:41:58.000Z","uid":78519,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"1a1b1fcedbc6704590dfb78aadfa63a5c815e9e2","tid":1927206,"uid":78519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-15T15:41:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.media.worldjournal.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/202003152330410491_45N201.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.media.worldjournal.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F03%2F202003152330410491_45N201.jpg&h=c9ee3d9c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">丹麥總理宣佈凡是受到新冠肺炎疫情衝擊、工作恐將不保者，丹麥政府將負責支付此人75%的薪水。（Getty Images）</span><br />\n<br />\n美國國家廣播公司報導，丹麥政府15日宣佈一項新協議，凡是受到新冠肺炎疫情衝擊、工作恐將不保者，丹麥政府將負責支付此人75%的薪水。<br />\n<br />\n丹麥總理梅特．佛瑞德里克森在記者會上說，這項政策將回溯到本月9日，持續到6月9日。<br />\n<br />\n佛瑞德里克森還呼籲企業不要裁員。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.worldjournal.com/6840467/article-%e8%b1%aa%e6%b0%a3%ef%bc%81%e4%b8%b9%e9%ba%a5%e7%85%a7%e9%a1%a7%e5%8f%97%e7%96%ab%e6%83%85%e8%a1%9d%e6%93%8a%e8%a1%8c%e6%a5%ad-%e5%b0%87%e8%b2%a0%e8%b2%ac%e4%b8%83%e6%88%90%e4%ba%94%e8%96%aa%e6%b0%b4/?ref=%E9%A6%96%E9%A0%81_%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82NOW\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.worldjournal.com%2F6840467%2Farticle-%25e8%25b1%25aa%25e6%25b0%25a3%25ef%25bc%2581%25e4%25b8%25b9%25e9%25ba%25a5%25e7%2585%25a7%25e9%25a1%25a7%25e5%258f%2597%25e7%2596%25ab%25e6%2583%2585%25e8%25a1%259d%25e6%2593%258a%25e8%25a1%258c%25e6%25a5%25ad-%25e5%25b0%2587%25e8%25b2%25a0%25e8%25b2%25ac%25e4%25b8%2583%25e6%2588%2590%25e4%25ba%2594%25e8%2596%25aa%25e6%25b0%25b4%2F%3Fref%3D%25E9%25A6%2596%25E9%25A0%2581_%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582NOW&d=ly5XvLwGuIZ6JSW2uqe%2BvmLTbr5529Gqcy%2B2MeRGono%3D&h=70c6ea0f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.worldjournal.com/6840467/article-%e8%b1%aa%e6%b0%a3%ef%bc%81%e4%b8%b9%e9%ba%a5%e7%85%a7%e9%a1%a7%e5%8f%97%e7%96%ab%e6%83%85%e8%a1%9d%e6%93%8a